pung <- mpsz %>%
  filter(PLN_AREA_N == "PUNGGOL")
pung <- pung%>%
  st_union()
pung <- st_make_valid(pung)

tamp <- mpsz %>%
  filter(PLN_AREA_N == "TAMPINES")
tamp <- tamp%>%
  st_union()
tamp <- st_make_valid(tamp)
